Dialogs.Dialog: Rinko
Hey, you...
What！？ Don't tell me you want a kiss on-the-go again！
Hah！？ What are you saying？
Even though we're newly weds, to do that everyday is just too embarrassing！
Are you still asleep or what！？
Ouch... Eh？ I think I got my dream mixed up with reality...
Rinko
I saw the news and there were people who got drifted to a faraway island and got rescued at last.
...Oh, I see. That's good to hear...
I know it's a good thing, but why did you look that relieved？ Are they someone you know？
No... But it'd be hard to be stuck there. If the rescue team hadn't gotten there, they would've been like Adam and Eve...
Adam and Eve？ Did you eat something wrong today？
Don't worry, I'll always protect you, ▲小早川＊▲！
Okay, okay. I'll have to go now, Adam.
Rinko
By the way, I found an abandoned cat...
You did？ Did it look exactly like you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Hah？ Did it look exactly like me？ You have that kind of taste, huh？
You must be imagining me with cat's ears and tail and stuff... Pervert.
(I shouldn't have mentioned it...)
Rinko
You know, my little brother likes to watch magical girl anime even though he's a boy...
Don't tell me it's the "Lucky Magical Girl Rinko"！
I don't think so... But do you also watch something like that？ And the name is Rinko...？
No, this Rinko is the daughter of a daruma doll！
...Never mind.
(I shouldn't have mentioned it...)
Did you play with dolls when you were a kid, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
I did. I usually stayed home alone...
You're not lonely now, right？
Nah... Now I've my father, mother, a little brother and friends... And you, too.
...I see. That's good then. Yeah, I'll never bring you sadness！
Why do you look like you are to burst into tears！？ I don't get it！
Rinko
Huh？ Somehow, I smell lavenders...
Lavender？ That's...
...She disappeared！ What？ How could that be？
Come back ▲小早川＊▲...！
Sorry for disturbing you. But Rinko has to go. Take care.
Rinko
Speaking of Volvavine...
You said Volvavine！？
...Yeah, but what's with that reaction？
You did great, Rintaro！ You and Volvavine will continue to use your power to protect the world. Go！ Volve~~~~
Shut up！ Volve Kick！
...Ouch... I'm glad it wasn't the missile...
You are the real you, right ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
What's with that？
This conversation might be a continuation of my dreams...
Hiya！
Did that wake you？
That hurts... Nope, not a dream...
Yeah？ Well, that's good.
Supposing... If I am to die all of a sudden, will you cry for me？
Rinko
I won't.
You didn't have to answer that quickly...
I won't cry for someone who likes to ask a stupid question.
Geez, stop talking about depressing what-if-nonsense situations already.
Rinko
You know, I watched the Killer Bambies DVD again...
Killer Bambies are really good！
Huh？ You know about them...？
You can feel the unity between the stage and the audience.
...You get it, huh？ But what I don't get is why you seem interested in them all of a sudden...
Rinko
Hey, you got a moment？
What's up？
I have some Valentine's chocolate for you. See？ I'm your girlfriend, after all.
Thanks！ I'm so happy.
...You don't have to be that happy. It's just an event.
But you gave this to me. That's why I'm so happy, ▲小早川＊▲.
In that case, waiting in a long line to buy this was worth the effort then.
You did that for me？
Well, I actually went to buy something else and just saw this, so...
I see. Thanks. I guess I don't have to think so much about a return gift for White Day.
...Ah, there's that event too. Well, I'll be waiting then.
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Ah... Don't pretend to be so calm. Rinko can see through your act clearly.
Are you talking about Valentine's Day？
If you have a girlfriend but you don't get any chocolate, it'd be very depressing, right？ That's why...
Yeah！
Are you going to give it to me？
It feels annoying to just give it to you like this. Can you say, "Please give me my chocolate, Rinko- sama"？
Hah！？
...Geez, I was joking！ Here you are.
Thanks...
I really didn't know what to pick, so I ended up with this... Bye！
(She's just trying to hide her shyness, huh？)
Rinko
Hey, you got a moment？
What's up？
Today's Valentine's Day, right？ I just thought that I'd bring some chocolate.
Will you give it to me？
Definitely. I'm your girlfriend, right？ Here.
Thanks.
By the way, it's homemade. Are you happy？
Homemade？ I see. You really tried your best...
I really went through a lot of trouble, so you'd better savor it, okay？ Hehe.
Ah, of course.
Yeah. Well... I can expect something on White Day, right？
Yeah, leave it to me.
Rinko
Wait...
What's up？
Here...
For me？ ...Could this be Valentine's chocolate？
I guess.
Really？ Thanks.
Nah, you've been taking care of me and stuff...
You also care about things like this, huh, ▲小早川＊▲？
Well, I think it's childish and just a business scheme to boost sales for certain occasions.
Yeah, that's certainly true.
This is all. Bye...
Today is White Day.
Rinko
Last month belonged to the guys and this month belongs to the girls, huh？ It's stupid to be so into these kinds of things.
Anyway, I feel so excited to give you a return gift, you know？
You were waiting for the right timing, huh？ That's why you're smirking like that.
Well, just be honest and take it.
Okay... Thanks.
(She seems extremely happy to receive it.)
I see. I'll take it then.
(I guess that's it.)
This...？
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Hey, isn't this kind of thing troublesome？
On Valentine's, did you also think that it was troublesome, ▲小早川＊▲？
Well... I didn't think it was.
Then I didn't think that it was troublesome either. Rather, it was fun.
Yeah... I really think I understand that feeling.
So, please take it.
Okay... I'll take it then. Hehe.
Rinko
Now, here's a question. What day is today？
White Day, right？ I know.
Hmm？ Did you prepare a return gift for me then？
Of course. Here.
You did！ Hehe.
(She seems extremely happy to receive it.)
Hmm... This is so-so.
(I guess that's it.)
I'm happy that you got something for me... But I'm not happy with this.
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Anyway, you remembering it makes me happier than the gift you gave me.
Hey, did you think the same when I gave you a Valentine's gift？
Well, that's true. It's just fun to give and to receive presents on events like these.
Yeah. After you prepare the gift, it's kind of a heart- throbbing moment to give it...
A heart-throbbing moment？ For you？
...I-I mean, in general.
What？
Rinko has never felt something like that.
Then I was the only one who experienced this heart- throbbing moment.
Eh！？ Well... Actually, Rinko kind of... Um...
(Did you feel it or not？)
Rinko
You got a minute, ▲主人公＊▲？
What a coincidence. I was about to go to see you, ▲小早川＊▲.
Well, because it's White Day？
Ah, yeah. I've prepared a return gift for you.
Okay, okay. I've been waiting.
Wow, thanks！ I'm really happy！
(She seems extremely happy to receive it.)
Thank you. I was looking forward to this！
(I guess that's it.)
I probably had my hopes too high...
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Now that it's ended, I feel a bit sad.
Why？
Because during events like this, it's fun to think about what I'll give and what I'll receive.
It's really fun, but it would be really hectic if we had events like these every month.
You don't have to splurge that much money on it, but... Nah, forget it.
If there are too many events in one year, they all will be less important.
Haha, that's true.
For me, I've already gotten a lot from you. You've already made Rinko happy.
You got a minute ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
...What is it？
I got a Valentine's return gift for you. Today's White Day.
...Did I give you any chocolate？
It isn't about returning a favor. I'm just giving it to you because I want to. But I don't know if you'll like it or not.
Ah... This is unexpectedly nice.
(She seems extremely happy to receive it.)
Hmm... This is just so-so.
(I guess that's it.)
..I don't know...
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
So, today's White Day, huh？ No wonder the girls seem restless.
You weren't looking forward to it at all, do you, ▲小早川＊▲？
I was, but I forgot about it.
I see. Many people use this occasion to confess their love, you know？
...Just so you know, I'm not really expecting something like that from this kind of occasion.
For me, I think this is a nice occasion to say thanks to the people who took care of you.
Hmm... Well, whatever you say.
(Oh no！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Rinko
Ah...
Um...
Sorry！ I totally forgot about White Day！
Eh？ No way...
I'm really sorry！
It's okay... Bye...
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Oh no！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Rinko
Hehe. Why are you making that stupid face for, ▲主人公＊▲？
Sorry！ I totally forgot about White Day！
No way！！
I'm really sorry！
...Idiot！
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Oh no！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Sorry！ I totally forgot about White Day！
Eh！？ So cruel！
I'm really sorry！
Geez, I won't listen. I was really looking forward to this...
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Oh no！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Rinko
Ah... What？
Sorry！ I totally forgot about White Day！
..It's okay. I wasn't expecting anything.
I'm really sorry！
I said it was okay. Bye...
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Well, today is the sports festival.)
What's wrong？ Are you not feeling well？
Rinko
Isn't that obvious？ It's the sports festival and I'm depressing.
Even if you aren't good at sports, you can still cheer for your friends.
...That's also troublesome.
At least try encouraging people who are joining in the events.
I'll give it a try.
Yeah！
(Yes！ Perfect！！)
Rinko
Hmm？ You did fairy well.
Yeah. Were you watching me ▲小早川＊▲？
Well, yeah. Wasn't that great？ That was something I really couldn't do.
(This is thanks to me for training regularly...)
(It was no good at all...)
Rinko
Hah...
Were you watching me... ▲小早川＊▲？
Well, you aren't very good at sports, huh...？
(I'll have to train some more...)
(Well, today is the culture festival.)
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
I heard that you'd be participating in the Most Handsome Man Contest, huh？
My friends put my name in it. I just knew about this a while ago...
Well, you have nothing to lose. Why don't you give it a try？
Don't say something like that... Anyway, why don't you join the Most Beautiful Woman Contest, ▲小早川＊▲？
...Are you kidding me？
Well？ I think you have a chance to win.
Stop it...
(Anyway, I'll just give it a try...)
(I won the contest...)
Rinko
...Hmm？ You did it.
Perhaps, you also think that I'm handsome, ▲小早川＊▲？
You shouldn't get ahead of yourself.
Well... Yeah, that's right.
Anyway, congratulations.
(It's good that I always take care of my appearance.)
(The contest result was totally no good...)
Rinko
Well, I guess that's it.
Yeah...
Don't feel down. That kind of contest doesn't matter.
Appearance isn't the only thing that measures human's charm.
You're right.
(But, I should've paid more attention to my appearance.)
Hmm, I'm getting excited...
Rinko
Ah, you're here...
Merry Christmas, ▲小早川＊▲！
We really don't have to say something like that...
Really？ Well, you look good with this dress.
It's just a normal dress.
Well, about the present...
Yeah, I've prepared it.
Really？ Hehe. Then let's exchange them...
Okay...
Ah... This is... Hehe, thank you.
(She seems extremely happy to receive it.)
Um... Okay, thanks.
(I guess that's it.)
Well... I'll just take it then...
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Speaking of which, about the present... Well...
Present？ Are we talking about Santa Claus？
...Hah. It's okay. Never mind...
(Urgh. I should've gotten something for her.)
Hmm... There's a place that I want us to go...
Well, I have to go home now...
I see. Bye...
Hmm, I'm getting excited...
Rinko
You're here！
Merry Christmas ▲小早川＊▲！
Ah, Merry... Whatever. We don't have to say that.
Haha. You're wearing a dress, huh...？ It suits you.
Don't say something so embarrassing.
Hey, I have a present for you.
Yeah, me too.
Then let's exchange them.
Okay...
Ah, this is what I've always wanted... This is great！
(She seems extremely happy to receive it.)
Hmm？ This one？ Thanks.
(I guess that's it.)
Huh？ Is this your present？
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Hey, about the present. What do we do？
Huh？ You still believe in Santa Claus ▲小早川＊▲？
That's not what I mean！ Idiot！
(Urgh. I should've gotten something for her.)
Hey, can you accompany me after this？
I'm tired. I'm going home...
Is that so？ Bye...
Hmm, I'm getting excited...
Rinko
Ah, Merry Christmas！
Merry Christmas！ You're wearing a dress today. It suits you.
Hehe... Thanks.
Hey, it's natural that we prepared a present for each other, right？
Yes, of course.
Yay. Okay, let's exchange them.
Oh...
Ah, this one. I've wanted it！ Thanks！
(She seems extremely happy to receive it.)
...Thanks. I'll cherish it.
(I guess that's it.)
...Yeah, just your feeling makes me happy.
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Hey！ What about the present！？
Haha, are you going to hang up a sock before you go to bed tonight？
Geez, that's totally not what I meant. You don't even know...
(Urgh. I should've gotten something for her.)
Hey, can you accompany Rinko a little bit after this？
Rinko can't stay until late. It's time to go home.
Okay, go home carefully...
Hmm, I'm getting excited...
Rinko
Ah...
Merry Christmas ▲小早川＊▲！
You don't seem to be excited about this.
It's just an annual event.
You don't even wear a dress？ It'd suit you.
I don't want to. It's too troublesome...
I'm going home... Bye...
Ah, see you later...
Hmm...？ When the lights are on, the atmosphere is totally different.
Rinko
They are just regular trees wrapped with some lights, but somehow they seem different.
Perhaps, you're also enjoying this, huh, ▲小早川＊▲？
...Why？
...Just a boyfriend's intuition.
What？ I don't know what you mean. The one who's enjoying it is you.
Maybe...
Yeah, you are. Rinko is cool about this.
But with such cold weather, someone so cool like Rinko could be frozen, you know？
Then I should make you feel warm. Come closer to me.
Come on...
Okay, I got it.
How is it？ Do you feel warm already？
Just a little more.
I see...
Hmm...
Yeah？
It'd be nice if we can also watch it like this together next year.
Yeah, that's right...
▲主人公＊▲.
What？
I love you...
Rinko
Hmm...？ Not only the scenery, but somehow the atmosphere's also different.
It really is a special day.
Will some miracles happen today？
I don't know. What kind of miracle are you expecting, ▲小早川＊▲？
Well, Rinko is a human. It's normal to have a few desires.
Desires...？ How about you leave it to Santa then？
Santa only visits the kids, right？ Anyway, he doesn't even exist.
Shall I take the role of Santa for you today？
Huh？ What are you trying to say...？ Fine. Just continue...
I might be able to make your wishes come true. Just tell me.
...But, there are a lot of things that Rinko wishes for.
Santa has saved some money, you know... Although it's not much.
Then...
Can you come closer to me？
Yeah...
...Eh？ What about your wishes？
You've already granted them...
Hmm...
▲主人公＊▲.
What？
I love you...
Rinko
Wow... It's the same normal scenery, but it just looks totally different when they put some lights on...
Yeah, it's like a different world.
Yeah, this is amazing... Also, it's amazing that I feel so warm to be with you...
Before I met you, I've never felt something like this...
Me neither. If I were alone, I'd just walk past this place without paying attention.
Say... What do you think about Rinko now？ Is Rinko a good girlfriend for you？
Yes, you have always been cute, but today you look the best ▲小早川＊▲.
Okay, thank you. But... You make me feel uneasy when you say something like that.
Why？
You say that Rinko has always been cute. That makes this current Rinko lose her self-confidence.
But, no matter what, it's the same you,right, ▲小早川＊▲？
This current Rinko is not the same as Rinko in the past. Ever since I met you, I've changed a lot.
...But in the past, you loved me, and now you still love me, right？
Of course...
No matter how much you've changed, I'll always love you ▲小早川＊▲.
Is this still not enough？
▲小早川＊▲？
Just now, Rinko has changed again.
Eh？
Now, I love you even more than before... And I will probably love you more and more after this....
▲主人公＊▲.
What？
I love you...
It's cold... Will she be here soon？
Rinko
Happy New Year.
Happy New Year. This year, please be nice to me, ▲小早川＊▲.
Okay.
The kimono looks good on you.
Thanks.
Now, let's go visit the shrine.
Rinko
I don't want my friends to see us like this.
Is it too embarrassing？
No. But, acting all flirty from the start of the year is pretty lame.
Lame, huh...？
It doesn't fit with Rinko's cool image. That's all！
As expected on New Year's, the shrine becomes just unusually crowded and we can hardly move.
Rinko
But since we are already here, we should at least offer our prayers.
You're right. We should try to move forward then.
Okay, let's go. If we don't hold hands, we might get lost.
By the way, how much should we give for the offertory？ Like, 10 yen？ Or 100 yen？
Well... People say that 5 yen is the minimum and 25 yen is the average and such...
Then you and Rinko should give 55 yen.
...Why？
It's a nice number, like a sign that we will always be equal.
Then let's do that.
Rinko
Then it's already time I go.
Oh, see you later.
Well...
Hm？
From now on, please take care of me.
Oh, take care of me too this year.
It sure is hot, even at night...
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
You look good in a yukata, ▲小早川＊▲.
Yeah, thanks.
So, let's head for the shrine.
Wow, this is exciting.
Rinko
Ah, candied apple...
Want to have some？
No, it's okay...
Really？ I'd like to buy one. Do you want to share？
...Yeah. Well, in that case, I'll eat it.
Rinko
Ah, they're carrying the portable shrine.
Yeah. They are doing their best carrying it.
Have you ever tried carrying it？
No, never... Are you interested to try？
I don't want to try it myself, but just looking would be fun.
You should try it while wearing the traditional loincloth.
...L-Loincloth...？
Rinko
Wow... Amazing...
It really is. I'm glad we came here.
Yeah. I thought that going to see fireworks would be boring, but seeing the real thing is different...
It's good that we came here.
...Yeah.
Well, we'd better check out the stalls first. Do you have anything you want to play or eat？
Rinko
Whatever is fine. The night is long anyway.
Right. Look, there's some goldfish catching.
Ah, I'm not into living animals... Caring for them will be a pain.
Then... How about that one？ The shooting gallery.
Hmm. The prizes don't interest me.
Well... We'll go for food then.
Yeah. That's more like it. Some delicacies are only served on festivals.
...Perhaps, you were aiming for the food stalls from the beginning, huh？
Not really. Well, maybe a little bit.
It's fine, it's fine. I want to grab a bite too.
In that case, you should have told me earlier. I have no choice now. I'll go with you.
They're also having the Bon festival dance.
Rinko
The Bon festival dance？ When I was little, I only danced with Dad and Mom...
I never knew the dance steps. I was just swaying my hands and trying to be one with the crowd.
The little Rinko... I wish I could've seen that, ▲小早川＊▲.
Yeah, lolicon.
You got that wrong！ Anyway, it's been quite a while since the last time you danced, right？
Yeah. It's been years since I participated.
So, want to have a go？
What？ No. Even now, Rinko still hasn't learned how to dance！
Just sway your hands and go with the flow. You can also follow me.
Geez... I am counting on you, okay？
Rinko
Oh, it has started already. We've got to hurry.
Right. Be careful. The stairway is pretty dark.
Okay, I know.
Wow... Beautiful...
A real find, right？ This spot has the best view for fireworks.
Yeah. A good spot.
A yukata, fireworks, and you. To Rinko, this might be the best combination.
What did you say？
I said the fireworks are beautiful.
Ah, right...
(I hope we'll be able to come here next year as well...)
Rinko
Well, I should go. Thanks...
I couldn't let you walk alone at night. I would be worried.
I see... Hehe.
Well, see you later.
It sure is hot, even at night...
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
You look good in a yukata, ▲小早川＊▲.
Yeah, thanks.
So, let's go to the Bay Bridge.
Rinko
Wow... Amazing...
It really is. I'm glad we came here.
Yeah. I thought that going to see fireworks would be boring, but seeing the real thing is different...
It's good that we came here.
...Yeah.
Rinko
Oh, it has started already. We've got to hurry.
Right. Be careful. The stairway is pretty dark.
Okay, I know.
Wow... Beautiful...
A real find, right？ This spot has the best view for fireworks.
Yeah. A good spot.
A yukata, fireworks, and you. To Rinko, this might be the best combination.
What did you say？
I said the fireworks are beautiful.
Ah, right...
(I hope we'll be able to come here next year as well...)
Rinko
Well, I should go. Thanks...
I couldn't let you walk alone at night. I would be worried.
I see... Hehe.
Well, see you later.
(Okay, the new semester starts today！)
The new semester starts today, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Even if you didn't tell me, I already knew that... Hah...
What？ You don't seem to be happy about the new semester.
Only happy-go-lucky people would be so cheerful about it...
(She didn't mean me, right...？)
(Today is the school's closing ceremony！)
Today's the last day of class ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Hey, why do you look so happy about it？
Because it's gonna be our school break.
It's good that you're happy, but we still have to work at the library.
(So the library opens during the break, huh...？)
(I think the test results have been announced...)
(I did perfectly for the tests this time.)
Rinko
Hmm？ You're pretty good at studying, huh...？
▲小早川＊▲.
For something like tests, you'd better try to get good results for them.
Yeah. And how about you？
...There are people who don't use academic tests to measure their own values, you know...
(So, how's your result then？)
(I think the test results have been announced...)
(The result isn't bad, but isn't good either... Quite mediocre...)
Rinko
Isn't it okay？ You got average grades.
▲小早川＊▲.
With these grades, it won't matter much if you do better or worse after this.
Do you think so？ How about your grades then？
Average.
(Average...？ How average then？)
(I think the test results have been announced...)
(I got really bad result from the exams this time...)
Rinko
...Someone looks depressing here.
Even if you got bad grades, nothing is going to change.
...I'll try to think like that. Anyway, how about your grades？
We're already done with the tests. It doesn't matter anymore, right？
(Is that so？ I think her grades are probably better than mine.)
Rinko
Hey. Well...
Is there anything you want, ▲小早川＊▲？
Today is... your birthday, right？ Happy birthday.
Thanks, ▲小早川＊▲.
I have no choice, right？ I'm your girlfriend, after all.
I'm really happy.
Anyway, I'm not sure if you'll like my present though.
It's something you chose for me. I'm sure I'll like it ▲小早川＊▲.
...That's good then... But, are you really happy？
Yeah. And I'm really grateful to you, ▲小早川＊▲...
Hehe...
Rinko
Wait... Hey.
Do you need something ▲小早川＊▲？
Today is your birthday, right？ So, happy birthday.
Thanks, ▲小早川＊▲.
Feel free to show your happiness. I even prepared a present for you.
A present？
Here you are！
Oh, thanks.
This is so out of character for me, so I won't forgive you if you aren't grateful.
Thanks so much. You've done so much for me, ▲小早川＊▲...
Ah, geez！ Why do you have to make me feel so embarrassed...？
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
What's up, ▲小早川＊▲？
Happy birthday. I wanted to be the first to say it to you. Did anyone beat me to it？
Don't worry. You're the first one, ▲小早川＊▲.
I see. That's good... Ah, I have a present for you too.
Really？ Thanks. I'm so happy.
I'm also happy to see your happy face.
I think people give presents so they can see other people's smiling faces.
That might be true...
Rinko
Hey...
Ah, what's the matter, ▲小早川＊▲？
Today... is your birthday, right？
...That's right！
Did you forget...？ Anyway, I'll give you this. Here you are.
You're giving me a gift！？ I've never imagined that this would happen. Thanks, ▲小早川＊▲.
Don't act so surprised！
I'm already impressed that you remembered my birthday.
I just happened to remember it. You're exaggerating...
Hey, ▲小早川＊▲.
